tv.amwa.maj.integer

Annotation Type Int32


  • @Documented
 @Target(value={FIELD,PARAMETER,METHOD})
public @interface Int32

    Labels a 32-bit 2's complement integer value. This annotation is used to show that a Java int value is being used to represent an AAF Int32 type value.

    Original C type name: aafInt32
    C base type: signed int
    Java base type: int

    See Also:
    TypeDefinitions.Int32, TypeDefinitions.Int32Array, Int32Array
